<p><strong>4. <a target="_blank" href="http://dapper.net/">Dapper</a></strong>
- Dapper allows anyone to create Dapps (widgets) that track the content
of any website. This can also be used to track the RSS feeds of sites
that do not offer one. In terms of features, Dapper has the most diverse
selection, but it does require a learning curve. Be sure to check out <a
	target="_blank" href="http://www.dappit.com/dapperfox/">DapperFox</a>
which is a Firefox extension that creates an RSS feed from any page.</p>
